{"tid":1923830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無國界記者利用 Minecraft 建「虛擬圖書館」　記載新聞封鎖事件及被禁報道內容","createTime":"2020-03-13T09:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T08:50:58.000Z","uid":75969,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"506293aed40cf43a8860c59290923ed5daff2a15","tid":1923830,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/library-19_1oR46_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flibrary-19_1oR46_1200x0.png&h=3f0a16fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞自由並非必然，一些專權國家就往往以資訊封鎖的方式阻止人民接觸真相，甚至傷害講出真相的人。為了以更生動的方式推廣，「無國界記者」（RSF）與專門以電腦遊戲《Minecraft》進行設計的工作室 BlockWorks 合作，興建了一個虛擬圖書館 The Uncensored Library，記載了俄羅斯、越南、沙特阿拉伯、墨西哥以及埃及的新聞封鎖事件，讓玩家和網民「進館」細閱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89489260_504958376817304_7576411508024803328_n_72ZOj_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89489260_504958376817304_7576411508024803328_n_72ZOj_1200x0.png&h=73a88e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBlockworks 找來了 16 個國家的 24 名 Minecraft 高手，用了超過 250 小時、1,250 萬 Minecraft 磚頭才建好這個虛擬圖書館。圖書館設有一個圓拱形大廳，訪客可以經大廳前往 6 個區域。在各個區域裡，訪客可以點擊書架上的書本，觀看那些被封鎖的新聞資訊。除了文章之後，還會有記者的語音檔可以收聽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_7j-Ynup6BM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_7j-Ynup6BM&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=bb23e079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_7j-Ynup6BM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89731624_2848164971946903_1448047489406992384_n_PltFW_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89731624_2848164971946903_1448047489406992384_n_PltFW_1200x0.png&h=520dbfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89681558_244826466543607_2791960138058039296_n_yzRmD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89681558_244826466543607_2791960138058039296_n_yzRmD_1200x0.png&h=b37f5409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果是 Minecraft 的玩家，他們可以透過官方網站來下載圖書館，並在《Minecraft》遊戲中以單人模式進入地圖。除此之外，他們也可以選擇直接連線，在線上伺服器與其他玩家交流。但如果不是 Minecraft 的玩家，無國界記者也準備了網頁版的圖書館給網民瀏覽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89352175_248633636150942_1170845678738341888_n_TAVmP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89352175_248633636150942_1170845678738341888_n_TAVmP_1200x0.png&h=3f094323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRSF 表示，希望透過 Minecraft 這個遊戲，讓世上每一個人，都可以知道新聞和資訊封鎖的問題。另外，他們特別關注年輕人如果受到資訊封鎖影響，將無法表達他們的意見，所以組織特別聚焦在電腦遊戲上，讓他們接收到獨立的資訊。RSF 表示，他們會不斷增加虛擬圖書館的館藏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/90030207_820600528459361_1554347182658682880_n_kMMo2_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F90030207_820600528459361_1554347182658682880_n_kMMo2_1200x0.png&h=55d9c3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立場新聞</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%84%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%8C%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8-minecraft-%E5%BB%BA-%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8-%E8%A8%98%E8%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E8%A2%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8-minecraft-%25E5%25BB%25BA-%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%25BC%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=e8ef9fcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8-minecraft-%25E5%25BB%25BA-%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%25BC%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9%2F&h=8e841198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%84%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%8C%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8-minecraft-%E5%BB%BA-%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8-%E8%A8%98%E8%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E8%A2%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"5eaf33892bb19b07e81bd67d33c97d2dc3335fcc","tid":1923830,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e632fc6aaddb5afcf83f5f5ef1a9e4598d156d1b","tid":1923830,"uid":84128,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"中國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e826e1c8adcccf74826905780fa2a9bbe4eb11db","tid":1923830,"uid":2445,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"記載了俄羅斯、越南、沙特阿拉伯、墨西哥以及埃及的新聞封鎖事件<br />\n<br />\n但無支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class